{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Animation.reverse()","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/Animation\"><code>Animation()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propiedades</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\"><code>currentTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/effect\"><code>effect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished\"><code>finished</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/id\"><code>id</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/pending\"><code>pending</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playbackRate\"><code>playbackRate</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState\"><code>playState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/ready\"><code>ready</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/replaceState\"><code>replaceState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime\"><code>startTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/timeline\"><code>timeline</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel\"><code>cancel()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/commitStyles\"><code>commitStyles()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish\"><code>finish()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause\"><code>pause()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/persist\"><code>persist()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/play\"><code>play()</code></a></li><li><em><code>reverse()</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/updatePlaybackRate\"><code>updatePlaybackRate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eventos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel_event\"><code>cancel</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish_event\"><code>finish</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/remove_event\"><code>remove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herencia</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Web Animations</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEffect\"><code>AnimationEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationPlaybackEvent\"><code>AnimationPlaybackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/getAnimations\"><code>Document.getAnimations()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/timeline\"><code>Document.timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentTimeline\"><code>DocumentTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Element/animate\"><code>Element.animate()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta es una <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">tecnología experimental</a></strong><br>Comprueba la <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Tabla de compabilidad de navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usarla en producción.</p></div></div>\n\n<p>El método <strong><code>Animation.reverse()</code></strong> de la interfaz <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a> Interface invierte la dirección de reproducción, lo que significa que la animación termina al principio. Si se llama en una animación sin reproducir, toda la animación se reproduce al revés. Si se llama en una animación pausada, continúa a la inversa.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxis","title":"Sintaxis","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">animation.reverse();\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parámetros","title":"Parámetros","isH3":true,"content":"<p>None.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor_devuelto","title":"Valor devuelto","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/undefined\"><code>undefined</code></a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplos","title":"Ejemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>En el ejemplo <a href=\"https://codepen.io/rachelnabors/pen/PNYGZQ?editors=0010\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Growing/Shrinking Alice Game</a> , hacer click o tocar la botella, hace que la animación de crecimiento de Alicia(<code>aliceChange</code>) sea reproducida al revés, lo que la hace más pequeña. Esto se hace estableciendo el&nbsp;<a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playbackRate\"><code>Animation.playbackRate</code></a> de <code>aliceChange</code>&nbsp; en <code>-1</code> de esta forma:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">shrinkAlice</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// reproduce la animación de Alicia al revés.</span>\n  aliceChange<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>playbackRate <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  aliceChange<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">play</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// reproduce la animación de la botella.</span>\n  drinking<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">play</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Pero también se podría haber hecho lamando a <code>reverse()</code> en <code>aliceChange</code> así:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">shrinkAlice</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// reproduce la animación de Alicia al revés.</span>\n  aliceChange<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">reverse</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// reproduce la animación de la botella.</span>\n  drinking<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">play</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificaciones","title":"Especificaciones","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/web-animations-1/#dom-animation-reverse\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Animations<br><small lang=\"es\">La definición de 'reverse()' en esta especificación.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad del navegador","id":"compatibilidad_del_navegador","isH3":false,"query":"api.Animation.reverse","dataURL":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_también","title":"Ver también","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a> para otros métodos y propiedades que puedes usar para el control de animaciones en páginas web.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause\"><code>Animation.pause()</code></a> para pausar una animación.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/play\"><code>Animation.play()</code></a> para reproducir una animación hacia adelante.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxis","id":"sintaxis"},{"text":"Ejemplos","id":"ejemplos"},{"text":"Especificaciones","id":"especificaciones"},{"text":"Compatibilidad del navegador","id":"compatibilidad_del_navegador"},{"text":"Ver también","id":"ver_también"}],"summary":"El método Animation.reverse() de la interfaz Animation Interface invierte la dirección de reproducción, lo que significa que la animación termina al principio. Si se llama en una animación sin reproducir, toda la animación se reproduce al revés. Si se llama en una animación pausada, continúa a la inversa.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Animation.reverse()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/api/animation/reverse","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/api/animation/reverse/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API","title":"Referencia de la API Web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation","title":"Animation"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse","title":"Animation.reverse()"}],"pageTitle":"Animation.reverse() - Referencia de la API Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}